# Status checklist and report schema

Canonical checklist and report schema for `/assistant:status`. Loaded by `commands/status.md`; validated by `evals/scripts/validate-fixtures.sh`.

## Checklist

```yaml
# Status check checklist — canonical check IDs, categories, and fix routing.

version: "0.1"

categories:
  - id: plugin
    title: Plugin install
  - id: profile
    title: Profile & personalisation
  - id: policies
    title: Policies
  - id: working-folder
    title: Working folder
  - id: always-on
    title: Scheduled jobs & reliability
  - id: connectors
    title: Connectors (advisory)
  - id: platform
    title: Platform fit

checks:
  # --- plugin ---
  - id: plugin-manifest-present
    category: plugin
    default_severity_on_fail: fail
    fix_ref: docs/guide/01-getting-started.md

  - id: plugin-skills-present
    category: plugin
    default_severity_on_fail: fail
    fix_ref: docs/guide/01-getting-started.md

